    <property key="submodel.description" value="Stack various probabilities maps into a map cube renaming each one according to the transitions present in the transition matrix. Probability maps must be ordered using a prefix like 1_ , e.g 1_filename.tif according to the number of the row of the respective transition.&#x0A;&#x0A;The map cube is used as input for both patcher and expander operators" />
